The paper deals with a computer vision problem of counting leaves from plant images using deep learning architectures. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of state-of-the-art deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves data-driven approaches, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
